description: Open Road Shaved Ice is doling out the most delicious icy treats, so perfect for defeating the Dallas heat. Each cone is created with shavings off a large block of ice, resulting in optimal snowy fluff and delight in every bite. Their plethora of hand-crafted fruity flavors are all preservative & high fructose corn syrup-free, and all quite delicious. If you’re hopin’ to indulge in a refreshing and tasty cone, just come on by to the Open Road Shaved Ice truck!
name: Open Road Shaved Ice
